    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear power band and 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip M-differential. The chassis integrity has been addressed with subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, following a recent rod bearing service. A purist-spec machine that balances raw performance with mechanical transparency.",
