    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in Alpine White with a Mocha Dakota leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and has been kept in a smoke-free, pet-free environment. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. The 19-inch alloy wheels are in great shape with no curb rash, wrapped in Continental tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin feels premium; the leather is supple and treated regularly, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the panoramic sunroof, Harman Kardon surround sound, and the iDrive navigation system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound with a full-service history performed at authorized centers. The most recent oil service and brake fluid flush were completed just 2,000 miles ago. It starts smoothly, shifts effortlessly, and provides the balanced, sporty ride you expect from a BMW. Includes two key fobs and all original manuals.",
